{"tid":1853873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習派軍抗疫「扼殺民亂於萌芽」","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:10:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":87,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"da1223309d36cb782dc684b5642408a4560eaffa","tid":1853873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/JZVZNA55UHYVGDVAKAA5E2MJCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2FJZVZNA55UHYVGDVAKAA5E2MJCQ%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5a9839c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2FJZVZNA55UHYVGDVAKAA5E2MJCQ%2F&h=40c89189\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/JZVZNA55UHYVGDVAKAA5E2MJCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n習派軍抗疫「扼殺民亂於萌芽」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200131/large/1580401813_d9ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200131%2Flarge%2F1580401813_d9ab.gif&h=13e18ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍醫療隊本月26日已奉命進駐武漢金銀潭醫院。新華社<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】黨和軍隊當下統一控制疫情，時事評論員劉銳紹分析稱，黨及軍隊全部都聽命於中共總書記兼軍委主席習近平，習欲藉此顯示他才是真正發號施令的抗疫指揮，做到「有功自己拎，有責李克強孭」。此外，湖北境內開始出現民怨民憤，軍隊管理可將民亂「扼殺於萌芽狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：編入Dirty Team 伊院ICU四護士劈炮<br />\n<br />\n李克強有責任無實權<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹昨向《蘋果》分析指，現時全國疫情失守，湖北省內居民在物價、在物資上極度不滿，加上其他省分人士亦發起堵路，杯葛武漢人，社會出現「民眾鬥民眾」，極嚴重的社會矛盾未來或演變成民變，影響政權，因此官方派遣強力部門，壓制零星民亂，將問題「扼殺於萌芽狀態」。劉又指，總理李克強雖然擔任防疫小組組長，但職位上只是「有責而無最大實權」，最大實權是擁有軍隊的習近平。現時黨及軍隊一調控疫情，包括建醫院及派軍隊醫護，習藉此顯示自己才是真正發號施令，真正的抗疫指揮。他日若疫情減退，將功在習；若抗疫失利，責任則落在防疫小組長李的身上，政治上做到「進可攻，退可守」。<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹認為中央亦知湖北官員已是負資產，知道「搵佢地死硬」，故中央軍隊進駐亦代表架空湖北高官。不過，他認為罪責不完全在湖北高官，而是中央早有指令要各地在春節假期衝一衝經濟，結果「上面要威，下面跪低」，以致地方政府隱瞞疫情。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"7b341904ee7d1da71f834075b3a0f5243e18e71c","tid":1853873,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n一齊收港共支共皮<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05f47f1f53e039d2c08490d7484453ff8230c5a3","tid":1853873,"uid":2054,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"屠城..."},{"pid":"4865721e1caa32301bbbf08e35541c0bb9f0ebb6","tid":1853873,"uid":14449,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"習敗北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81da3c564f58c36ecb0fa16c1ad5582716edda2","tid":1853873,"uid":283587,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"即係已有民亂"},{"pid":"4ee6bf6118e5e2ccdc1fef6adf94e4d150d8f55c","tid":1853873,"uid":19353,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"出軍隊先正 1隻感染到帶返巢穴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c9138e2707d945bd77999dc256b58c56e72c79","tid":1853873,"uid":8911,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"同啲蟻藥一樣，番去傳播"},{"pid":"85d66b7ba1d00c8eb923dcbf9204f87521600afc","tid":1853873,"uid":8014,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"湖北咁大唔信無黑市武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c9e55223acd5190d28529f92248ba3